{"title":"Silca Strip Chip promises one-stop-shop for waxing factory fresh chains","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/silca-strip-chip","date":1708438093000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/silca-strip-chip\">Silca Strip Chip promises one-stop-shop for waxing factory fresh chains</a></p>\n\n<p>Silca has released its latest maintenance product in the form the Strip Chip, which claims to turn factory lubes into a wax coating. Silca says this is the ‘first ever in-wax chain degreaser’ and is cleaner, faster and better for the environment. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Strip Chip has been launched alongside Silca’s Ultimate Chain Wax System, a one-stop kit with all the products needed for waxing your chain. </p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-bike-chain\">Best bike chain: How to choose a replacement chain</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/silca-hot-wax-x-chain-lube\">Silca claims new £220 Hot Wax X chain lube saves 12 watts and lasts 800km</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tutorials/watch-how-to-fit-a-press-fit-bottom-bracket\">Watch: How to fit a press-fit bottom bracket</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<h2>How does it work? </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Silca Strip Chip Wax chain cleaning\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-122-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Silca</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Strip Chip uses a process called Oleogelation, traditionally used in the food industry. Silca says that it converts oils that would generally act as solvents, such as factory chain lube, into binders that connect with wax chain molecules. The Strip Chip replaces any white spirit or methylated alcohol needed to remove the factory grease, removing a step in the process of waxing a brand new chain. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>To use, you add one square of the Strip Chip to Silca’s hot melt wax (it’s not specified whether it will work with other brands), and then add the new chain. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>One stop pot</h2>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-123-647x970.jpg\" alt=\"Silca Strip Chip Wax chain cleaning\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-123-647x970.jpg 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-123-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-123-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-123-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-123-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-123-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-123-1140x1710.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/silca_strip_chip_wax-123-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /><figcaption>Silca</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Silca has also released its Ultimate Chain Wax System, which includes all the accessories needed for chain waxing, including a hanger and chain coupler and, in Silca’s words, ‘looks more dialled than your ole crockpot setup’.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/silca-strip-chip\">Silca Strip Chip promises one-stop-shop for waxing factory fresh chains</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Charlotte Head &#124; Tech Writer","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"43cd2313885c36c8f24fb0f5a701262bafb27e57840cbd1b86594f8844eaa355","category":"Cycling"}